{File:TSLA_IS.txt  Index:3  Index Date:20191008  PL:80.95%  PS:19.05%  Trades:21  CL:1}

IF CLOSE OF 8 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 4 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 4 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 5 DAYS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 5 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 7 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 7 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 6 BARS AGO
THEN BUY NEXT BAR ON THE OPEN WITH
PROFIT TARGET AT ENTRY PRICE + 3.1898402 %
AND STOP LOSS AT ENTRY PRICE - 3.5371906 %
